{"tid":2443033,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–老鼠的習性","createTime":"2021-03-11T20:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T03:57:11.000Z","uid":38861,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0afd7eff740e1689a2d7d6bb42e8d35288e50765","tid":2443033,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:14:42.000Z","msg":"老鼠與人類均是雜食性動物(Omnivores)，而老鼠每日約有80%的食物均是在晚上進食的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNNZnkv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNNZnkv.jpg&h=381c83d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n若果晚上(&gt;12hr)不讓老鼠進食的話，牠們的體重平均來說會減去10%左右。<br />\n<br />\n約連續22小時不讓牠們進食後，牠們腸道便會變得空空如也。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）老鼠是夜行性(Nocturnal)動物，牠們眼球內負責辨認顏色的錐體少得非常可憐，純粹依靠感應紫外線的接受器，透過紫外線的強弱了解世界。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gniYCTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgniYCTU.jpg&h=b946a39c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只不過的是，牠們大多偏愛清晨時份進行交配行為。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）老鼠的感覺毛 (Whiskers)有著感測聲音的能力，其排列大多是五橫行分佈，每行約有五至九點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hqL2kB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hqL2kB.png&h=95f274a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越靠近嘴部的感覺毛，所能感測的聲音頻率亦越高。<br />\n<br />\n人類最高能感測至20k Hz的音頻，而老鼠最高則能去到90k Hz，高於20k Hz的超聲波(Ultrasound)同時亦是老鼠聽力最為敏感的區域。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利用超聲波驅逐或者招來老鼠，或許可行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=64ac43e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=20a8029c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。"},{"pid":"52af5c0ae7f380e24c6cda1723fd9a7d35be4bd7","tid":2443033,"uid":15336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:17:23.000Z","msg":"Pish<br />\n題目既範圍都幾廣闊"},{"pid":"7dd74bb332b71fba5c892a29f7dea0c69fbdc16f","tid":2443033,"uid":199689,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:17:39.000Z","msg":"超音鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad38739d40dbac4368226640b2e211c7b09bdf4d","tid":2443033,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546b843ee55484d1012bdc3ca326ccf07077b4f9","tid":2443033,"uid":153808,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:48:12.000Z","msg":"用咩方法捉老鼠最好？<br />\n依加返工個到 3日捉左2隻老鼠<br />\n老鼠籠都唔夠用"},{"pid":"be7c64febddd4e9eaf86ff31f7030ca767d006d8","tid":2443033,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"546b843ee55484d1012bdc3ca326ccf07077b4f9","tid":2443033,"uid":153808,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:48:12.000Z","msg":"用咩方法捉老鼠最好？<br />\n依加返工個到 3日捉左2隻老鼠<br />\n老鼠籠都唔夠用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:49:56.000Z","msg":"唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541