貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:24:59.000Z","msg":"我驚隻貓驚老鼠多啲 啲老鼠捉唔哂"},{"pid":"2989942a9685a1762496a4bccf99868db5d1382f","tid":2443033,"uid":37796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"546b843ee55484d1012bdc3ca326ccf07077b4f9","tid":2443033,"uid":153808,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:48:12.000Z","msg":"用咩方法捉老鼠最好？<br />\n依加返工個到 3日捉左2隻老鼠<br />\n老鼠籠都唔夠用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:09:38.000Z","msg":"用踩板式老鼠籠/老鼠夾<br />\n放係牆腳邊<br />\n暗位(最好燈，太陽照唔到既位)<br />\n<br />\n佢地揀地方有d似貓<br />\n中意角落<br />\n中意暖既地方(例如紙箱，綿被之類)<br />\n中意高<br />\n<br />\n初生細隻個d 攀爬力冇咁好<br />\n用老鼠膠都捉到<br />\n但成年個d 醒d 同大力就冇咁易<br />\n又會爬得高<br />\n老鼠籠要放埋高位<br />\n<br />\n老鼠其實唔係咁好芝士<br />\n最中意係花生醬，瓜子，葵花籽之類果仁類又夠香既野<br />\n用呢d 做餌"},{"pid":"eaf7f8dc71a624706177f16994d9de0b5c9b3018","tid":2443033,"uid":37796,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0894ae2b78434b9f9aa550995d5f4484bf3f303e","tid":2443033,"uid":210612,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"546b843ee55484d1012bdc3ca326ccf07077b4f9","tid":2443033,"uid":153808,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:48:12.000Z","msg":"用咩方法捉老鼠最好？<br />\n依加返工個到 3日捉左2隻老鼠<br />\n老鼠籠都唔夠用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:00:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6SIlYiiCGLI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6SIlYiiCGLI&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=babc580f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6SIlYiiCGLI</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:11:57.000Z","msg":"呢啲要係open area/穀倉咁大既地方 先work<br />\n你睇下mouse trap monday 最新個幾集去左室內捉"},{"pid":"e3fc017675de9dcdfc84208da1497503d2f9b9b6","tid":2443033,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T01:12:56.000Z","msg":"用20年來同期/同一溫度濕度嘅心腦血管病死亡人數，你對比，可唔可以證明病人是否打完疫苗後死亡？"},{"pid":"6d689200ea986516f96914a3860fe0fb58ef9d10","tid":2443033,"uid":37796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0afd7eff740e1689a2d7d6bb42e8d35288e50765","tid":2443033,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T20:14:42.000Z","msg":"老鼠與人類均是雜食性動物(Omnivores)，而老鼠每日約有80%的食物均是在晚上進食的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNNZnkv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNNZnkv.jpg&h=381c83d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n若果晚上(&gt;12hr)不讓老鼠進食的話，牠們的體重平均來說會減去10%左右。<br />\n<br />\n約連續22小時不讓牠們進食後，牠們腸道便會變得空空如也。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）老鼠是夜行性(Nocturnal)動物，牠們眼球內負責辨認顏色的錐體少得非常可憐，純粹依靠感應紫外線的接受器，透過紫外線的強弱了解世界。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gniYCTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgniYCTU.jpg&h=b946a39c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只不過的是，牠們大多偏愛清晨時份進行交配行為。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）老鼠的感覺毛 (Whiskers)有著感測聲音的能力，其排列大多是五橫行分佈，每行約有五至九點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hqL2kB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hqL2kB.png&h=95f274a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越靠近嘴部的感覺毛，所能感測的聲音頻率亦越高。<br />\n<br />\n人類最高能感測至20k Hz的音頻，而老鼠最高則能去到90k Hz，高於20k Hz的超聲波(Ultrasound)同時亦是老鼠聽力最為敏感的區域。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利用超聲波驅逐或者招來老鼠，或許可行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=64ac43e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9